title: Baz Luhrmann classic launches in London's West End
text:
Baz Luhrmann classic launches in London's West End 2:43am GMT - 01:43 
'Strictly Ballroom', Baz Luhrmann's breakout 1992 film, has been adapted for the stage in London's West End. Rough Cut - no reporter narration. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
